name: Justice for Pnut and Fred
description: The coin embodies their vision and shared purpose, symbolizing their unique bond and mission. Through this project, Fred and Peanut aim to bring justice and recognition to their efforts, creating a platform that not only entertains but also uplifts their story and the values they stand for. It’s more than just a meme coin—it’s a statement of solidarity, innovation, and the pursuit of justice for Fred and Pnut.
